James Robison Hays III

Age : 39Public asset : 1,459,693 USDLinked companies :  Ashford Hospitality Trust, Inc. -  Ashford Hospitality Prime Inc -  Ashford Inc 





Summary 



Mr. James R. Hays, III, is Chief Investment Officer at Ashford Investment Management LLC, Chief Strategy Officer at Ashford Hospitality Prime, Inc. and Ashford Hospitality Trust, Inc. and Senior Vice President-Finance & Strategy at Ashford Hospitality Advisors LLC.He is on the Board of Directors at Ashford, Inc.He sets Ashford Investment Management's industry views and capital market expectations while overseeing asset allocation and security selection within the portfolio.Prior to Ashford, he worked in the Corporate Development Group at Dresser, Inc. and in the Global Power and Energy Investment Banking unit at Merrill Lynch.^He holds an A.B. in Politics from Princeton University and studied philosophy at the Pontifical University of the Holy Cross in Rome.



